    "7 Cosmological collider physicsWe now turn our attention back to the cosmological collider physics set-up and derive properties of the bulk-bulk propagator.",
    "We do not find it necessary to discuss the power spectra and bulk-boundary propagators here since they are not required for our needs and details can be found in [5].",
